.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

City: new-york, rome, paris, liverpool, miami
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, scientist, manager, software-developer, social-worker
House: wooden, art-deco, modern, tower, gothic-revival
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: superhero, comedy, time-travel, scientific, horror
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: dahlia, tulip, orchid, marigold, zinnia
1. the dressmaker is the person traveling to paris
2. the swedish is the person who growsorchid
3. the scientist is the tower house
4. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool
5. the person traveling to rome is the art-deco house
6. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who growstulip
7. the person traveling to miami is the person watching comedy movies
8. the modern house is in the middle
9. the software-developer is on the far left
10. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia
11. the person who growszinnias is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies
12. the person watching superhero movies is the wooden house
13. the manager is the person watching scientific movies
14. the software-developer is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york
15. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| City		|    miami	|     new-york	|      paris	|     rome	|     liverpool	|
| Job	|   software-developer	|    scientist	|    dressmaker	|    manager	|    swedish	|
| Flower		|     dahlia	|    zinnia	|     tulip	|     marigold	|      orchid	|
| House	|    gothic-revival	|     tower	|     modern	|    art-deco	|      wooden	|
| Movie-Genre		|   comedy	|    horror	|  time-travel	|    scientific	|   superhero	|
